<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.1.5">
<l>koṇṭa tāḷuṟi kōlak koṭumaḻu</l>
<l>taṇṭi ṉarpaṟi yōlaic cayaṉattar</l>
<l>viṇṭiṉ mullai yarumpaṉṉa palliṉa</l>
<l>raṇṭar miṇṭip pukuntuney yāṭiṉār</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who collected the pole, the stick of the rope-shelf,</l>
<l>and the cruel axe that had been grasped,</l>
<l>those who have a palm-leaf mat for a bed,</l>
<l>those who have teeth like jasmine buds that have not blossomed,</l>
<l>[and] the cowherders gathered and entered the [village] and bathed with ghee.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
